theorem mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff_of_field (B : Type _) [CommRing B] [Algebra A B] [IsLocalization S B]
    (x : K) :
    x ∈ (map_to_fraction_ring K S B hS).range ↔ ∃ (a s : A)(hs : s ∈ S), x = algebraMap A K a * (algebraMap A K s)⁻¹ :=
  by
  rw [mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff]
  iterate 3 congr with ; convert iff.rfl; rw [Units.val_inv_eq_inv_val]; rfl
#align mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff_of_field mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff_of_field
mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `non_zero_divisors -/
theorem mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff (B : Type _) [CommRing B] [Algebra A B] [IsLocalization S B]
    (hS : S ≤ non_zero_divisors A) (x : K) :
    x ∈ (map_to_fraction_ring K S B hS).range ↔ ∃ (a s : A)(hs : s ∈ S), x = IsLocalization.mk' K a ⟨s, hS hs⟩ :=
  ⟨by
    rintro ⟨x, rfl⟩
    obtain ⟨a, s, rfl⟩ := IsLocalization.mk'_surjective S x
    use a, s, s.2
    apply IsLocalization.lift_mk', by
    rintro ⟨a, s, hs, rfl⟩
    use IsLocalization.mk' _ a ⟨s, hs⟩
    apply IsLocalization.lift_mk'⟩
#align mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff mem_range_map_to_fraction_ring_iff

@[simp]
theorem map_to_fraction_ring_apply {B : Type _} [CommRing B] [Algebra A B] [IsLocalization S B]
    (hS : S ≤ non_zero_divisors A) (b : B) :
    map_to_fraction_ring K S B hS b = IsLocalization.lift (map_is_unit_of_le K S hS) b :=
  rfl

theorem map_is_unit_of_le (hS : S ≤ non_zero_divisors A) (s : S) : IsUnit (algebraMap A K s) := by
